general.description:
Jamstack Conf Virtual Is Back!

This year Jamstack Conf is a virtual event celebrating the next generation of web apps, where the Jamstack community and ecosystem comes together to learn, connect and create.¬† We‚Äôll cover the future of Jamstack for many use cases, including new innovations, demos and case studies.




Schedule (Pacific - PDT)

View the full catalogue of talks here.

Tuesday, Oct 6, 9:00 am - 4:00 pm PDT


Keynotes: State of the Jamstack, and how the Jamstack powers the ACLU
Breakout talks & lightning talks: Real-time Satellite Tasking on the Jamstack, How Teespring has 2x conversion, How Kleppiere migrated 98 sites to the Jamstack to increase performance and cost savings, In Search of Jamstack Search, Migrating to Netlify One Page at a Time, Touring Next.js, and more!
Interactive topic tables: Jamstack E-Commerce, Jamstack at the Edge, Accessibility, and more!
1:1 attendee networking
Jamstack Expo + product demos
Community Celebration


Wednesday, Oct 7, 9:00 am PDT

Paid workshops will take place on October 7th. All workshops start at 9 am PDT, and attendance is limited. Please only register for one workshop.


Getting Started with GatsbyJS
Building Modern APIs with GraphQL
Build a Better Build Plugin
Building from Scratch with Nuxt.js
Jamstack for E-Commerce




Tickets

Jamstack Conf Virtual conference sessions will be FREE¬†on October 6th, thanks to our sponsors. Workshops on October 7th are $100, and availability is limited. We look forward to bringing together thousands of global Jamstack community members for this virtual event!
